latestPosts.caption: We won our first Gold Award for our English Lemon at the Fancy Food Show in NYC in 2007.  We have made this 6 pack for Costco - arrived in Bay Area and hits Texas tomorrow and San Diego region, CO, NV, Los Angeles & Hawaii next week. My favorite- tart lemon curd contrasting with buttery cake. Serve with creme fraiche. 😊. Costco made me change the name but I quite like what I came up with.  xx.  #costco #lemoncake #lemon #desserts #englishbaking. #whats_in_your_cart @whats_in_your_cart
